From: Kalash Nainwal <kalash@nexthop.ai>
Date: Mon, 13 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Enable sharpd daemon for testing

Enable sharpd (Super Happy Advanced Routing Process) daemon
for route injection testing and development purposes.

Signed-off-by: Kalash Nainwal <kalash@nexthop.ai>
---
 debian/rules | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/debian/rules b/debian/rules
index 74573c9a0..212c5122a 100755
--- a/debian/rules
+++ b/debian/rules
@@ -63,6 +63,7 @@ override_dh_auto_configure:
 		--enable-doc-html \
 		--enable-snmp \
 		--enable-fpm \
+		--enable-sharpd \
 		--disable-protobuf \
 		--disable-zeromq \
 		--enable-ospfapi \
